menuconfig SENSOR_TRIGGER
	bool "Sensor trigger channel (zbus)"
	depends on ZBUS
	help
	  Enables the sensor_trigger_chan zbus channel. Any publisher
	  (timer, button, MQTT) can fire a sensor_trigger_event; each fake
	  sensor driver independently listens and publishes to
	  sensor_event_chan when triggered.
